Package semsim.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaseInsensitiveComparator
    Convenience class for performing case-insensitive comparisons between Strings
    DuplicateChecker
    Utility class for finding and removing duplicate instances of the same annotation in two models The duplicate instance is replaced with the instance in the first model This allows for much faster comparisons during the mapping phase of a merge
    ErrorEntry
    An entry in a SemSim ErrorLog
    ErrorLog
    Class for storing errors that may occur when processing models and associated data
    ResourcesManager
    Class for reading files either outside or inside the SemSim package and organizing the info in lookup tables, reference sets, etc.
    SemSimComponentComparator
    Comparator for comparing the names of SemSimObjects, ignoring case
    SemSimCopy
    Methods for performing a deep copy of the structures in a SemSim model.
    SemSimUtil
    A collection of utility methods for working with SemSim models
